{
  "page_title": "获取收款项目的商户单号",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "获取收款项目的商户单号",
      "api_name": "get_payment_info",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/externalpay/get_payment_info",
      "description": "获取对外收款项目中每笔收款的商户单号",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "调用接口凭证"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "payment_id",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "收款项目单号。在发起对外收款中返回。"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "返回码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "对返回码的文本描述内容"
        },
        {
          "name": "bill_list",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "收款单号列表。每笔支付对应一个收款单号"
        },
        {
          "name": "bill_list[].out_trade_no",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "收款单号"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "请求包体示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n   \"payment_id\":\"xxxx\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "返回结果示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"errcode\": 0,\n\t\"errmsg\": \"ok\",\n\t\"bill_list\": [\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"out_trade_no\":\"xxxx\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"out_trade_no\":\"yyyy\"\n\t\t}\n\t]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "调用的应用需要满足如下的权限，且只允许获取由应用本身创建的收款项目的收款单号列表\n\n- 自建应用：配置到「对外收款- 可调用接口的应用」中\n- 代开发应用：具有「对外收款」权限\n- 第三方应用：具有「对外收款」权限\n\n*注：* 从2023年12月1日0点起，不再支持通过系统应用secret调用接口，存量企业暂不受影响 [查看详情](https://developer.work.weixin.qq.com/document/51165)"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}